{
  "uid": "cb-tuning",
  "title": "Circuit Breaker 튜닝",
  "description": "Resilience4j 서킷브레이커 임계값(slow/failure rate, min-calls, window) 튜닝 의사결정 전용 대시보드. 분포 측정·통계적 외삽·평가 메커니즘 가시화에 책임 범위 한정. 비용/일반 API RPS 등 운영 모니터링은 별도 대시보드 책임.",
  "tags": [
    "circuit-breaker",
    "tuning",
    "resilience4j"
  ],
  "timezone": "browser",
  "schemaVersion": 39,
  "version": 1,
  "refresh": "30s",
  "time": {
    "from": "now-30d",
    "to": "now"
  },
  "timepicker": {
    "refresh_intervals": [
      "30s",
      "1m",
      "5m",
      "15m",
      "1h"
    ]
  },
  "templating": {
    "list": [
      {
        "name": "rate_window",
        "type": "custom",
        "label": "Rate Window",
        "query": "5m,15m,1h,6h,24h,7d",
        "current": {
          "text": "1h",
          "value": "1h"
        },
        "options": [
          {
            "text": "5m",
            "value": "5m",
            "selected": false
          },
          {
            "text": "15m",
            "value": "15m",
            "selected": false
          },
          {
            "text": "1h",
            "value": "1h",
            "selected": true
          },
          {
            "text": "6h",
            "value": "6h",
            "selected": false
          },
          {
            "text": "24h",
            "value": "24h",
            "selected": false
          },
          {
            "text": "7d",
            "value": "7d",
            "selected": false
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "name": "quiz_type",
        "type": "query",
        "label": "Quiz Type",
        "datasource": {
          "type": "prometheus",
          "uid": "PBFA97CFB590B2093"
        },
        "query": "label_values(quiz_generation_outcome_total, quiz_type)",
        "includeAll": true,
        "multi": true,
        "current": {
          "text": "All",
          "value": "$__all"
        }
      }
    ]
  },
  "panels": [
    {
      "id": 200,
      "type": "row",
      "title": "2. TTFQ Distribution (measured + estimated)",
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 0,
        "w": 24,
        "h": 1
      },
      "collapsed": false
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "title": "TTFQ measured (p50 / p95)",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 1,
        "w": 12,
        "h": 8
      },
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "PBFA97CFB590B2093"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.50, sum by (le) (rate(gemini_request_first_quiz_duration_seconds_bucket[$rate_window])))",
          "legendFormat": "p50 (measured)"
        },
        {
          "refId": "B",
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.95, sum by (le) (rate(gemini_request_first_quiz_duration_seconds_bucket[$rate_window])))",
          "legendFormat": "p95 (measured)"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "s"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "title": "TTFQ estimated p99 (log-normal vs Pareto α=2.21)",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 12,
        "y": 1,
        "w": 12,
        "h": 8
      },
      "description": "log-normal: 30s 이하 분포 fit. Pareto: 30s 초과 꼬리 fit (Heavy-tail 보강). slow threshold=60s 선 표시.",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "PBFA97CFB590B2093"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "exp(ln(histogram_quantile(0.95, sum by (le) (rate(gemini_request_first_quiz_duration_seconds_bucket[$rate_window])))) * 1.4136 + ln(histogram_quantile(0.50, sum by (le) (rate(gemini_request_first_quiz_duration_seconds_bucket[$rate_window])))) * -0.4136)",
          "legendFormat": "p99 (log-normal estimate)"
        },
        {
          "refId": "B",
          "expr": "30 * ( ((sum(increase(gemini_request_first_quiz_duration_seconds_count[$rate_window])) - sum(increase(gemini_request_first_quiz_duration_seconds_bucket{le=\"30.0\"}[$rate_window]))) / sum(increase(gemini_request_first_quiz_duration_seconds_count[$rate_window]))) / 0.01 ) ^ (1/2.21)",
          "legendFormat": "p99 (Pareto estimate)"
        },
        {
          "refId": "C",
          "expr": "30 * ( ((sum(increase(gemini_request_first_quiz_duration_seconds_count[$rate_window])) - sum(increase(gemini_request_first_quiz_duration_seconds_bucket{le=\"30.0\"}[$rate_window]))) / sum(increase(gemini_request_first_quiz_duration_seconds_count[$rate_window]))) / 0.001 ) ^ (1/2.21)",
          "legendFormat": "p99.9 (Pareto estimate)"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "s",
          "custom": {
            "thresholdsStyle": {
              "mode": "line"
            }
          },
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "transparent",
                "value": null
              },
              {
                "color": "red",
                "value": 60
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 7,
      "title": "Slow threshold exceedance ratios (%)",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 9,
        "w": 12,
        "h": 8
      },
      "description": "30s 직접 측정 + 60s Pareto 외삽. 1% 선이 임계 위험 신호.",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "PBFA97CFB590B2093"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "100 * (sum(increase(gemini_request_first_quiz_duration_seconds_count[$rate_window])) - sum(increase(gemini_request_first_quiz_duration_seconds_bucket{le=\"30.0\"}[$rate_window]))) / sum(increase(gemini_request_first_quiz_duration_seconds_count[$rate_window]))",
          "legendFormat": "P(TTFQ>30s) measured"
        },
        {
          "refId": "B",
          "expr": "100 * 2^(-2.21) * (sum(increase(gemini_request_first_quiz_duration_seconds_count[$rate_window])) - sum(increase(gemini_request_first_quiz_duration_seconds_bucket{le=\"30.0\"}[$rate_window]))) / sum(increase(gemini_request_first_quiz_duration_seconds_count[$rate_window]))",
          "legendFormat": "P(TTFQ>60s) Pareto estimate"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "percent",
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "green",
                "value": null
              },
              {
                "color": "yellow",
                "value": 0.7
              },
              {
                "color": "red",
                "value": 1.0
              }
            ]
          },
          "custom": {
            "thresholdsStyle": {
              "mode": "line"
            }
          }
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 8,
      "title": "TTFQ _max observed (heavy-tail watch)",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 12,
        "y": 9,
        "w": 12,
        "h": 8
      },
      "description": "실측 max 추적. 119s baseline 초과 시 fat-tail 심화 시그널.",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "PBFA97CFB590B2093"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "max by (max_chunks) (max_over_time(gemini_request_first_quiz_duration_seconds_max[$rate_window]))",
          "legendFormat": "max_chunks={{max_chunks}}"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "s",
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "transparent",
                "value": null
              },
              {
                "color": "orange",
                "value": 119
              },
              {
                "color": "red",
                "value": 180
              }
            ]
          },
          "custom": {
            "thresholdsStyle": {
              "mode": "line+area"
            }
          }
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 400,
      "type": "row",
      "title": "4. Trigger-related Signals (CB 입력 정합성)",
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 17,
        "w": 24,
        "h": 1
      },
      "collapsed": false
    },
    {
      "id": 14,
      "title": "Quiz generation outcome (record-exceptions 정합성)",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 18,
        "w": 12,
        "h": 7
      },
      "description": "fail/partial이 GeminiInfraException으로 CB에 카운트되는지 검증. failure-rate 임계(30%) 산정 근거.",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "PBFA97CFB590B2093"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "sum by (outcome, quiz_type) (rate(quiz_generation_outcome_total{quiz_type=~\"$quiz_type\"}[$rate_window]))",
          "legendFormat": "{{quiz_type}}/{{outcome}}"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "ops",
          "custom": {
            "stacking": {
              "mode": "normal"
            }
          }
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 15,
      "title": "Streaming timeout rate (slow=60s vs 5min cap 관계)",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 12,
        "y": 18,
        "w": 12,
        "h": 7
      },
      "description": "5min timeout이 slow=60s 임계보다 먼저 발동하는지 검증. timeout이 잦으면 slow 임계 하향 검토.",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "PBFA97CFB590B2093"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "sum by (quiz_type) (rate(gemini_streaming_timeout_total{quiz_type=~\"$quiz_type\"}[$rate_window]))",
          "legendFormat": "{{quiz_type}}"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 500,
      "type": "row",
      "title": "5. System Resources (fake-slow 배제)",
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 25,
        "w": 24,
        "h": 1
      },
      "collapsed": false
    },
    {
      "id": 18,
      "title": "JVM heap used + GC pause",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 26,
        "w": 12,
        "h": 7
      },
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "PBFA97CFB590B2093"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "sum(jvm_memory_used_bytes{area=\"heap\"})",
          "legendFormat": "heap used"
        },
        {
          "refId": "B",
          "expr": "rate(jvm_gc_pause_seconds_sum[$rate_window])",
          "legendFormat": "gc pause/s"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "bytes"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 19,
      "title": "HikariCP connections (active / pending)",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 12,
        "y": 26,
        "w": 12,
        "h": 7
      },
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "PBFA97CFB590B2093"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "hikaricp_connections_active",
          "legendFormat": "active"
        },
        {
          "refId": "B",
          "expr": "hikaricp_connections_pending",
          "legendFormat": "pending"
        },
        {
          "refId": "C",
          "expr": "hikaricp_connections_max",
          "legendFormat": "max"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 600,
      "type": "row",
      "title": "6. Burst Pattern (sparse + burst 혼재 평가 발동성)",
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 33,
        "w": 24,
        "h": 1
      },
      "collapsed": false
    },
    {
      "id": 20,
      "title": "Calls per minute (burst detection, 1m window)",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 34,
        "w": 12,
        "h": 7
      },
      "description": "1분 윈도우 RPS (gemini TTFQ 호출). 평시 baseline ~0.0002 ops 대비 burst peak 가시화. 빨간 라인=720s window×5min-calls 도달에 필요한 ops(0.0083).",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "PBFA97CFB590B2093"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "sum(rate(gemini_request_first_quiz_duration_seconds_count[1m]))",
          "legendFormat": "1m rate"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "ops",
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "transparent",
                "value": null
              },
              {
                "color": "yellow",
                "value": 0.0083
              }
            ]
          },
          "custom": {
            "thresholdsStyle": {
              "mode": "line"
            }
          }
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 21,
      "title": "Evaluation active timeline (≥5 calls in 720s)",
      "type": "state-timeline",
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 12,
        "y": 34,
        "w": 12,
        "h": 7
      },
      "description": "12분(=720s) 윈도우에 호출 5건 이상 들어온 시점=CB 평가 발동 가능 구간. 1=활성, 0=비활성. 자체 측정 메트릭 기반.",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "PBFA97CFB590B2093"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "(sum(increase(gemini_request_first_quiz_duration_seconds_count[12m])) >= bool 5)",
          "legendFormat": "evaluation_active"
        }
      ],
      "options": {
        "showValue": "auto",
        "mergeValues": true
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "mappings": [
            {
              "type": "value",
              "options": {
                "0": {
                  "text": "INACTIVE",
                  "color": "dark-orange"
                }
              }
            },
            {
              "type": "value",
              "options": {
                "1": {
                  "text": "ACTIVE",
                  "color": "green"
                }
              }
            }
          ]
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 22,
      "title": "Burst event count ($__range, ≥5 calls in 720s window)",
      "type": "stat",
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 41,
        "w": 8,
        "h": 5
      },
      "description": "선택 시간 범위 내 평가 발동 진입(=버스트) 횟수. 0이면 임계 자체가 발동 가능했던 적 없음 → 임계 수치 튜닝 무의미.",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "PBFA97CFB590B2093"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "sum(changes(((sum(increase(gemini_request_first_quiz_duration_seconds_count[12m])) >= bool 5))[$__range:1m])) / 2",
          "instant": true
        }
      ],
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ]
        },
        "colorMode": "background"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "red",
                "value": null
              },
              {
                "color": "yellow",
                "value": 1
              },
              {
                "color": "green",
                "value": 5
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 23,
      "title": "Peak RPS vs baseline ($__range)",
      "type": "stat",
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 8,
        "y": 41,
        "w": 8,
        "h": 5
      },
      "description": "burst peak (1m max) ÷ 평균 RPS = burst 비율. 비율이 높을수록 평시 통계로 임계 산정 위험.",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "PBFA97CFB590B2093"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "max_over_time(sum(rate(gemini_request_first_quiz_duration_seconds_count[1m]))[$__range:1m])",
          "legendFormat": "peak (1m max)"
        },
        {
          "refId": "B",
          "expr": "sum(rate(gemini_request_first_quiz_duration_seconds_count[$__range]))",
          "legendFormat": "baseline (mean)"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "ops"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 24,
      "title": "Evaluation active time ratio ($__range)",
      "type": "stat",
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 16,
        "y": 41,
        "w": 8,
        "h": 5
      },
      "description": "선택 범위에서 평가가 활성화 가능했던 시간 비율. 1% 미만이면 사실상 항상 평가 비활성 = 임계값이 99% 시간대에 무의미.",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "PBFA97CFB590B2093"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "100 * avg_over_time(((sum(increase(gemini_request_first_quiz_duration_seconds_count[12m])) >= bool 5))[$__range:1m])",
          "instant": true
        }
      ],
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ]
        },
        "colorMode": "background"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "percent",
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "red",
                "value": null
              },
              {
                "color": "yellow",
                "value": 1
              },
              {
                "color": "green",
                "value": 10
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      }
    }
  ],
  "annotations": {
    "list": [
      {
        "name": "Circuit OPEN events",
        "datasource": {
          "type": "prometheus",
          "uid": "PBFA97CFB590B2093"
        },
        "enable": true,
        "iconColor": "red",
        "expr": "resilience4j_circuitbreaker_state{name=\"aiServer\", state=\"open\"} == 1",
        "titleFormat": "aiServer OPEN"
      }
    ]
  }
}